title: Sobha Realty Concludes FY 2025 with AED 30 Billion in Sales, Marking 30% Growth Over 2024
content: Sobha Realty Concludes FY 2025 with AED 30 Billion in Sales, Marking 30% Growth Over 2024
short_summary: Sobha Realty reported strong financial performance for fiscal year 2025, achieving AED 30 billion in sales. This represents a 30% increase compared to the previous year (2024), demonstrating significant growth in the company's real estate business.
